<h2 id="sample-sentiment-analysis-projects">Sample Sentiment Analysis Projects</h2>

<p><strong>NaSent ‚Äì Stanford‚Äôs Neural Analysis of Sentiment</strong>
Analyzes sentences from movie reviews and gauges the sentiments they express on a five-point scale from strong like to strong dislike. Experiment with the online demo at <a href="https://nlp.stanford.edu/sentiment/">https://nlp.stanford.edu/sentiment/</a></p>

